## 运行命令

```bash
# .env 配置 AMAP_MAPS_API_KEY 后
docker compose up -d
.venv/bin/python3.14 server/main.py

curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" "http://127.0.0.1:8000/geo/me?ip=114.114.114.114"
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m pytest server/api/geo_test.py -v
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m pytest server/api -v
.venv/bin/python3.14 examples/03_amap_mcp_demo.py
```

## 验收标准

- [ ] `GET /geo/me` 返回 IP 对应省/市/天气
- [ ] Agent 可调用 `maps_ip_location` + `maps_weather`
- [ ] Web 登录后 header 显示城市/天气
- [ ] `docs/knowledge/mcp-amap.md` 存在且 README 为 done
